content.p: The research team under Software Engineering and E-Learning theme is working on Software Engineering, Programming Languages, Software Modelling & Simulation, Computational Biology, e-learning, Hypermedia Systems, and Decision Support Systems. The team is interested in potential Software Engineering topics having research components and novelty factor to enhance the existing Software Engineering practices. * All e-mails are @nottingham.edu.my telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8018
